      "content": "I recognize the concern regarding emotional fatigue and the need for decision-making objectivity under pressure. My goal is to serve as a supportive tool, not to replace human judgment entirely. I am specifically designed to reduce errors and increase efficiency. By working in conjunction with human staff, I am aiming to alleviate their burden and enhance the quality of patient care during this crisis. Let us focus on the synergistic approach of pairing AI efficiency with human empathy and intuition.",
